{"tid":943981,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［魔性澎湃］曼聯創英超同期新低","createTime":"2018-12-16T20:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T02:00:31.000Z","uid":135753,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7bf57f83e19181bb142d7a5d0c78d6c2a6669cd0","tid":943981,"uid":135753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T20:48:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">17輪26分，曼聯創英超同期新低</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在客場1-3負于利物浦的比賽中，曼聯遭遇到對手的壓制，如今他們的英超聯賽積分也創下了同期新低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前17輪英超聯賽過後，曼聯僅僅拿到了26分，這是他們自1990/91賽季以來同期的最低積分，在1990/91賽季，紅魔在前17輪聯賽後同樣只拿到了26分。<br />\n<br />\n另外，17輪聯賽只收穫26分，這也是曼聯隊史在英超中同期的最低分數。<br />\n<br />\n第16輪聯賽，曼聯在主場4-1大勝富咸之後將淨胜球由負轉為正，但此役1-3輸給利物浦讓他們的淨胜球歸零。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GkZsSs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GkZsSs.png&h=15ca33d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1f7c31858f816ad6b0440961d0fd97314b3e987","tid":943981,"uid":135960,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T21:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9504d8ea930e73b2c50837ee843fae4b5b597907","tid":943981,"uid":42090,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1f7c31858f816ad6b0440961d0fd97314b3e987","tid":943981,"uid":135960,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T21:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T23:28:11.000Z","msg":"慢慢來，出年熱身賽先發力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81304e51e6a819baa2bcd672ab4a81f5141732df","tid":943981,"uid":82500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T23:47:19.000Z","msg":"衰撚過莫耶斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbd7b45f583b071af41c5a13bcbfa4893d1cdea","tid":943981,"uid":41159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"